{% block bodyContent %}

    <h2 class="govuk-heading-m">When to book</h2>

    <p>Most discoveries last around 12 weeks.</p>

    <p>You should plan to book your peer review so that it happens near the end of discovery.</p>

    <p>You need to give at least 5 weeks notice to allow the Service Assessment team time to arrange the peer review panel.</p>

    <h2 class="govuk-heading-m">How to book</h2>

    <p>Only Department for Education staff can book a discovery peer review online.</p>

    <div class="dfeuk-action-link">
        <a class="dfeuk-action-link__link" href="https://request-manage-disco-pr.herokuapp.com/book/" target="_blank">
