            </svg>
            <span class="dfeuk-action-link__text">Book a peer review online</span>
        </a>
    </div>

    <p>Once your request has been submitted, you'll also be able to <a href="/service-assurance/book-a-discovery-peer-review/manage">manage your request online</a>.</p>

